Class
Description
Administrator
Represents an Administrator in the Hospital Management System (Hms) Inherits from Staff and implements the User interface Provides functionalities for managing hospital staff, appointments, and inventory
Appointment
Manages patient appointments in the hospital system.
AppointmentManagement
Manages appointments for doctors in the Hospital Management System (HMS).
AppointmentOutcomeRecord
Manages appointment outcomes, including recording and viewing details like service types, prescribed medications, and consultation notes
BillingDetails
Manages billing details for patients in the hospital system.
Doctor
Represents Doctors in the Hospital Management System (HMS).
ExportData
Provides functionality to export or display patient records in a structured format.
HospitalManagementSystem
Main class for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
InventoryManagement
Manages the inventory of medications in the hospital system.
MedicalRecordManagement
Manages medical records for patients, including viewing and updating records Integrates with appointmnets to ensure medical records are tied to valid appointments
Medication
Represents a medication in the pharmacy inventory system.
Patient
Represents a patient in the hospital system.

Represents a pharmacist in the hospital system.
Prescription
Represents a prescription in the pharmacy system.
Staff
Represents a staff member in the hospital system.
StaffManagement
Manages staff members in the hospital system.
User
Represents a user in the Hospital Management System (HMS).
